    {
      "time": 15.63,
      "time_str": "00:15.630",
      "text": "陈沁：是否对你承诺了太多",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 18.12,
      "time_str": "00:18.120",
      "text": "还是我原本给的就不够",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 23.13,
      "time_str": "00:23.130",
      "text": "阿穆：你始终有千万种理由",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 25.72,
      "time_str": "00:25.720",
      "text": "我一直都跟随你的感受",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 30.52,
      "time_str": "00:30.520",
      "text": "闪烁：让你疯 让你去放纵",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 34.66,
      "time_str": "00:34.660",
      "text": "以为你 有天会感动",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 37.94,
      "time_str": "00:37.940",
      "text": "关于流言 我装作无动于衷",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 49.84,
      "time_str": "00:49.840",
      "text": "阿穆+闪烁：直到所有的梦已破碎",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 52.52,
      "time_str": "00:52.520",
      "text": "才看见你的眼泪和后悔",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 57.42,
      "time_str": "00:57.420",
      "text": "陈沁：我是多想再给你机会",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
